landmark roe vs. wade decision, based woman's constitutional right privacy, said woman's decision abortion first three months pregnancy must left doctor.
court said states may interfere abortion decision second trimester protect woman's health, may take steps protect fetal life third trimester fetus survive outside womb.
state authority regulate abortions first trimester made absolute, however.
